  "keyFeatures": [
    "Bun monorepo with three apps: Hono backend, React admin SPA, Astro storefront",
    "Full product catalog with multi-currency pricing, images, and hierarchical categories",
    "Guest and authenticated checkout with server-side price calculation and atomic stock decrement",
    "Manual payment confirmation workflow (Zelle, bank transfer, cash on delivery)",
    "Order lifecycle state machine: pending_payment → paid → preparing → shipped → delivered / cancelled",
    "Role-based access control with Better Auth (customer / staff / admin)",
    "Drizzle ORM with PostgreSQL and full migration support via drizzle-kit",
    "Admin dashboard for managing products, orders, payments, categories, shipping rates, and users",
    "OpenAPI/Swagger UI served at /api/v1/docs",
    "Optimistic-concurrency order status transitions with audit history"
  ],
